Package: okeanos.stooq
Type: Package
Title: Fetch free financial time series from stooq.com
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Artur Wegrzyn
Maintainer: Artur Wegrzyn <awegrzyn17@gmail.com>
Description: Fetch financial data from Stooq (https://stooq.com/).
    This package provides simple interface for fetching of the time series
    in the format available on Stooq by ticker and for uer-defined time intervals.
    Legal disclaimer: I do not own the data fetched by this package. 
    That data is property of stooq.com or Stooq's data providers and can be only 
    used under terms and conditions defined at: https://stooq.com/terms.html .
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
